{"tid":591162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[溜冰] Evgenia BB正式宣布因傷退出世錦賽","createTime":"2018-03-13T09:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T06:34:59.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0153e280e0397f25e2344cf6c57bbb7d5cc7be","tid":591162,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.espn.com/olympics/figureskating/story/_/id/22742893/foot-injury-rules-evgenia-medvedeva-figure-skating-worlds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.espn.com%2Folympics%2Ffigureskating%2Fstory%2F_%2Fid%2F22742893%2Ffoot-injury-rules-evgenia-medvedeva-figure-skating-worlds&d=pBSnc7Ak3Aq9zpuZKNn22jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b101c692\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.espn.com/olympics/figureskating/story/_/id/22742893/foot-injury-rules-evgenia-medvedeva-figure-skating-worlds</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Foot injury rules Evgenia Medvedeva out of figure skating worlds</strong><br />\n<br />\nMOSCOW -- Olympic figure skating silver medalist Evgenia Medvedeva has withdrawn from the world championships later this month, ending the prospect of another showdown for gold with her friend and rival Alina Zagitova.<br />\n<br />\nThe Russian Figure Skating Federation says Medvedeva has a recurrence of the foot injury which kept her out of the Grand Prix Finals last December.<br />\n<br />\nDuring the Olympics, Medvedeva said the injury didn't bother her as she lost to Zagitova by 1.31 points for the gold medal.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, the Russian federation now says Medvedeva &quot;had to fight painful sensations while skating at the Olympics&quot; and doctors have ordered her to strictly limit any jumps from her injured foot for at least four weeks &quot;in order to avoid possible surgical intervention.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThat makes Zagitova the clear favorite for gold at the March 21-25 championships in Milan.<br />\n<br />\nGet well soon BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yS78gvm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyS78gvm.png&h=1e9795c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e120024b07a263c236179c734c8a7863b9e89244","tid":591162,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"ebfa92c9632c1e2e4cfa8bc07c7a89025837157c","tid":591162,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e120024b07a263c236179c734c8a7863b9e89244","tid":591162,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"文啊冚家剷"},{"pid":"7943ae6f78500aac5f9570977404219af7d154e4","tid":591162,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"怕輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dadc8984064d5b454ce638cf20e3dc3379c188","tid":591162,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7943ae6f78500aac5f9570977404219af7d154e4","tid":591162,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"怕輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:18:33.000Z","msg":"輸都輸過兩次啦，咁叫怕輸，你都on99, 咁講羽生都係怕輸啦"},{"pid":"53f31ba90c9de0cf5bbf42fa26640638195fb2ab","tid":591162,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5291b198f27ae6153ccc0b0d6a02d4f889180